## Non-Negotiable Standards

- **UK English** in all code comments, exception messages, and logs
- **Multi-tenant isolation** — every EF Core query must go through global query filters; never bypass them
- **Clean Architecture** — keep Domain pure; no EF Core or HTTP references in the Domain layer
- **Async-only** — no `.Result`, `.Wait()`, or blocking calls; propagate `CancellationToken` everywhere
- **Result pattern** — use `Result<T>` / `Result` for expected failures; reserve exceptions for truly unexpected errors
- **Nullable reference types** enabled (`<Nullable>enable</Nullable>`); eliminate all `?` suppressions (`!`)
